column16: John Hicks lines into a double play, third baseman Cheslor Cuthbert to second baseman Christian Colon.   Ketel Marte doubled off 2nd.
Shawn O'Malley walks.   Ketel Marte to 2nd.
Ketel Marte singles on a line drive to right fielder Alex Rios.
Jesus Sucre grounds out, shortstop Alcides Escobar to first baseman Drew Butera.
Robinson Cano grounds out, second baseman Omar Infante to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
Logan Morrison homers (9) on a line drive to right field.
Mike Zunino flies out softly to left fielder Alex Gordon.
Brad Miller flies out to left fielder Alex Gordon.
Dustin Ackley lines out to center fielder Lorenzo Cain.
Kyle Seager lines out to right fielder Alex Rios.
